sequenceDiagram
  participant S as Scheduler
  participant SAP as SAP Connector
  participant K as Kafka
  participant T as Transformation
  participant F as FinSight
  participant R as Reconciliation
  S->>SAP: Request GL delta using last token
  SAP-->>S: Batch metadata and next token
  SAP->>K: Publish extracted records
  K->>T: Consume records
  T->>T: Transform and validate
  T->>F: Batch upsert with idempotency key
  F-->>T: Accepted and rejected counts
  T->>R: Submit batch metrics
  R->>R: Compare counts, totals, checksums
  R-->>S: Reconciled
  S->>SAP: Commit delta token

